Anselm Tupper Nye, Sr.

Birth9 NOV 1797Org.1835-1881 Marietta, Marietta College, TrusteeOccup1836-1841Marietta MayorOccup1849-1849Marietta MayorDeath5 OCT 1881Grave

Aged: 83.9 years

Was a Mayor of Marietta, Ohio for two different terms totaling seven years:

1836-1841, 1849

His father Ichabod was also a mayor of Marietta for many years:

1811-1813, 1820-1821

His grandson-in-law's father, Daniel H. Buell, was mayor on two different occasions:

1825, 1842-1843
